{"tid":752594,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"「生物學」運動，睡眠，營養，戒咖啡因","createTime":"2018-07-23T02:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T03:19:07.000Z","uid":123335,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"39d1da34b9f4e96ce846a5b9c80de7388ba8a8b0","tid":752594,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"厭倦了沉淪既生活<br />\n飲酒，水煙，過飽，少眠，重度咖啡因，低運動量 ... etc <br />\n我厭倦了<br />\n<br />\n人生必須要作出改變<br />\n<br />\n黎緊30日 (7月23-8月23) <br />\n一改以往惡習<br />\n每日運動（重訓, 帶氧, HIIT) ，足夠睡眠（7.5hrs)，營養均衡，戒酒戒茶戒咖啡<br />\n<br />\n希望有一點點既細微改變"},{"pid":"fc2aea363c21d922dbaf2dea5184f81a5db2ae29","tid":752594,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"以往每日咖啡因量係400mg, <br />\n大約每日四杯咖啡"},{"pid":"8ee18875987e1ff3c39d308e564072a81b87cfa3","tid":752594,"uid":123335,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"以往呢種沉淪狀態<br />\n疲勞一直積累<br />\n只係不斷尋求短暫既刺激<br />\n刺激過後就係無盡既疲勞<br />\n唔會有前途"},{"pid":"91c3ae688ef31461407b0e1e991a9eb9b3aa7f8c","tid":752594,"uid":123335,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"呢個台開Post 好似寫blog 咁"},{"pid":"b0a97a81ad0a5cdbdd8669a2bdc52896fa6ed088","tid":752594,"uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n<br />\n源於無飲任何咖啡因飲料，<br />\n接近中午時，開始有輕微頭痛<br />\n<br />\n正在飲大量清水，希望舒緩痛楚"},{"pid":"9f43cd89673a4a45c84fb979b18d23ad9e53db56","tid":752594,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n<br />\n早餐自己煮<br />\n早餐：香蕉 ， 淨意粉（50g 乾重量），雞蛋兩隻"},{"pid":"5f5700279b6b250c03df1269809c6ad7c6539b82","tid":752594,"uid":147433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0a97a81ad0a5cdbdd8669a2bdc52896fa6ed088","tid":752594,"uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n<br />\n源於無飲任